<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/alex-davies-jones> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Alex Davies-Jones was Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Ministry of Justice from 9 July 2024 to 12 May 2026. She was elected as the MP for Pontypridd in July 2019."@en .
